snippet.title: Nidhogg 2 Comes to PS4 and Steam August 15 2017!
snippet.description:
Pre-Order now for PS4 https://store.playstation.com/#!/en-us/games/nidhogg-2/cid=UP2143-CUSA07640_00-NIDHOGG2GAMEPLAY

The wurm has returned and it must feed! Shed your garments and paint the walls with the flesh of your enemies, for only one can be worthy of sacrifice. 

store.steampowered.com/app/535520/Nidhogg_2/

Coming August 15, 2017

Trailer music by Mux Mool
